You know how Schrödinger put a cat in a box where it was both alive and dead until someone looked?

That's literally your bag of shitcoins right now.

Every token in your wallet exists in a quantum state: worth millions AND worthless until you check your balance.

The moment you look at your wallet? Reality collapses. You're either booking that Dubai trip or applying to your local McDonald's.

$MAYBE is the first memecoin that doesn't just embrace this truth – it's built on it.

Remember: Every shitcoin is a 100x until you check your wallet. (Ser, your portfolio only dumps when you observe it 🧠)
